sentences.sContent: Her new book is several notches above anything else she has written.
sentences.sCn: 她的新书比她的其他作品高出了好几个等级。

sentences.sContent: Jackson raised his voice by a notch.
sentences.sCn: 杰克逊将嗓音提高了一度。

sentences.sContent: The Spartans turned it up a notch in the second half.
sentences.sCn: 斯巴达人队在下半场中比分有所提高。
